metadata.name: Chibi Chill-Chan
metadata.description:
I don’t mind spending time alone
I kinda like my chill days
But girl I keep thinking about you lately
You've been on replay in my mind
And I don't mind.

Forever is a long time
But I keep my words that I say to you
Cause no matter what they say
I will fall for you.
:))

*Notes :
10th Illustration from "Chibi -Chan" series.
Illustrated & animated on Adobe Ps.
1800pxl x 2250pxl - 10fps
150 frame (Loop) - .MP4
1/1 #Loredangoo
